{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 490641, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 102076, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re : dz的父母应该会埋怨dz", "timestamp": 1603726031, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 490645, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 102076, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "会安慰cz，鼓励cz和朋友聊天/锻炼/主动治疗，告诉cz保研失败找不到工作退学也没关系quq\n", "timestamp": 1603726049, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 490649, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 102076, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "抱抱dz，相信父母会体谅自己的呀quq", "timestamp": 1603726080, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 490651, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 102076, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "之前我说状态很差哭着跟妈妈打电话，妈妈虽然安慰我的话蛮笨拙的但是有问我需不需要治疗，需不需要她跑来陪我", "timestamp": 1603726084, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 490655, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 102076, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "就是保研的时候我说我哭得停不下来没办法复习妈妈说那就别学习了", "timestamp": 1603726128, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 490658, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 102076, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "他们有时候也不是真的不关心就是很笨拙吧，不懂什么叫抑郁症，不懂自己该说什么做什么比较好", "timestamp": 1603726181, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 490660, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 102076, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "dz父母离异，高四压力太大有些焦虑都被妈妈嫌弃“为什么就你这样”", "timestamp": 1603726195, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 490670, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 102076, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我妈也一样，只会觉得是你的问题", "timestamp": 1603726422, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 490887, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 102076, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "开始会不理解，觉得是自己太脆弱。但是如果跟他们解释几句、表达一下自己状态差到什么程度（譬如失眠、自残倾向），他们会重视起来，然后明确地告诉他们你的需求——心理咨询或者去医院做检查，他们会帮你找资源去做的", "timestamp": 1603729131, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 490994, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 102076, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "会给我灌（鸡精+水） :)", "timestamp": 1603730411, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 491400, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 102076, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Bob说的是绝大多数情况，Francis做过fdy接触过的样本比较大", "timestamp": 1603764741, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 1, "pid": 102076, "reply": 11, "tag": null, "text": "如果得了抑郁症，父母会怎么对待你", "timestamp": 1603725983, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782636, "url": "", "vote": {}}}